ou are able to take your laptop with you, we still highly recommend to backup your photos at two places.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-backup-travel-photos-online\">Backup travel photos online<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Get your laptop online and your photos will be uploaded to the cloud automatically, even while you&#x2019;re away. Nothing easier than that.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/06\/23165500\/backup-photos-traveling-salt-in-our-hair-pinterest-456x600.jpg\" alt=\"backup photos while traveing\"><\/noscript><img class=\"alignnone size-large lazypreload\" alt=\"backup photos while traveing\" width=\"1094\" height=\"1440\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/06\/23165500\/backup-photos-traveling-salt-in-our-hair-pinterest-456x600.jpg 456w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/06\/23165500\/backup-photos-traveling-salt-in-our-hair-pinterest-300x395.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/06\/23165500\/backup-photos-traveling-salt-in-our-hair-pinterest-600x790.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/06\/23165500\/backup-photos-traveling-salt-in-our-hair-pinterest-257x338.jpg 257w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/06\/23165500\/backup-photos-traveling-salt-in-our-hair-pinterest-615x810.jpg 615w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/06\/23165500\/backup-photos-traveling-salt-in-our-hair-pinterest-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/06\/23165500\/backup-photos-traveling-salt-in-our-hair-pinterest-124x163.jpg 124w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/06\/23165500\/backup-photos-traveling-salt-in-our-hair-pinterest-137x180.jpg 137w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.